rComments: He's my TA but he does a way better job of teaching the material than any of my professors. I wish there were more of him so that the school could replace all the physics and math profs with an army of Marcs.

Despite his quizzes are difficult (as they are full of concepts), he teaches the course content extremely well. I have a very hard time understanding physics but he makes it a whole lot easier for me, and he responds to emails and is very accessible for help.

Marc is the best TA I've ever had. Physics is hard at the best of times, but he makes his lessons fun. His quizzes are really hard, but once you figure out that all you have to do is listen during his lesson, he just puts questions from his lesson on it.  You can tell he really cares about us by do all these extra things. Switch in if you can!
